{"tid":1388582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728義士心聲","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:38:38.000Z","uid":265682,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"043355929a09d40052dfc6145c412f292329ffba","tid":1388582,"uid":265682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"入到嚟同我推左佢先<br />\n我唔想再有義士陣亡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢聽到義士講<br />\n咩齊上齊落呀<br />\n咩一齊走<br />\n屌你728前線點解比人捉<br />\n???有冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心企得前線就唔好自己跑左去啦<br />\n留底第一排嘅自己走<br />\n連背囊都唔拉<br />\n有人跌左落地下都無視<br />\n踩過佢就算<br />\n好野<br />\n咩叫齊上齊落<br />\n咩叫一齊走<br />\n如果你地路過拉埋跌底嘅走<br />\n一定唔會49個被捕<br />\n下次可唔可以真係做到齊上齊落呀<br />\n我知有人一定話起碼拉少d人<br />\n但係知唔知咁樣搞到前線同你班仆街冇晒信心<br />\n企得前線就要預左齊上齊落<br />\n成班義士好撚傷心<br />\n以上所講全部屬實 你可以唔信 當我分化撚<br />\n我冇嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbee625a95ddaa18b1b5a4c528d6547ca3a909f7","tid":1388582,"uid":265682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"214ea497a1dde3c96475431d52f07b676671ba2f","tid":1388582,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"我地都係香港人，我願意罷工"},{"pid":"08e57d270fe48060dcae1783af59d21705387b9f","tid":1388582,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:36:21.000Z","msg":"一萬人都唔夠果幾十人鬥。醒下啦香港人"},{"pid":"382722efc241d4f395b2ad05a9dca70999570b09","tid":1388582,"uid":265682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor